{"tid":2236352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"比利時2間電訊商棄用中共華為 為歐洲安全網絡打響頭炮","createTime":"2020-10-09T11:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T12:05:36.000Z","uid":21470,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d17c347dd8b09f8595996898e199de5955143090","tid":2236352,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:36:41.000Z","msg":"比利時2間電訊商棄用華為 選用諾基亞發展5G<br />\n<br />\n比利時兩間電訊公司，放棄華為而選用諾基亞，發展5G流動網絡，成為歐洲首批棄用華為5G設備的商業電訊商；華為表示，接受比利時電訊商的決定，認為是基於自由市場原則，又強調華為向比利時供應設備超過10年，對當地的承諾會維持不變。<br />\n<br />\n美國致力游說盟友，不要使用華為設備，指存在竊密風險，不利雙方交流情報；歐盟總部設及歐洲議會設在比利時首都布魯塞爾， 令美國情報機構更關注比利時的5G建設。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2360933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2360933&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=1bce91c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2360933</a>"},{"pid":"b5c887cb237542a9ff4b380162f5766a7d82ca84","tid":2236352,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fa916128dab4d13af9e819eb4694f4f370ad7e","tid":2236352,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"之前唔係仲有？"},{"pid":"21fb27d0875c4fccd6364963e42020ff64f73c35","tid":2236352,"uid":82394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:53:38.000Z","msg":"比利時<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fff7a4d02951e64f4393bbd71b38cc2afe455bb","tid":2236352,"uid":244759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔到電訊供應商唔轉，如果持續制裁華為，令到佢營運唔到，就算今年同你買左設備，下年你比人制裁到執笠，無曬零件同後勤，到時咪又係要轉，咁我不如而家就轉左先。"},{"pid":"18801a570df8fe5981cf653e906bfc2100b8b0f2","tid":2236352,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T11:59:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d45edd8e8a289d03fd0c8ded7afc81ae002008b","tid":2236352,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73080c61d6f75dc72600e582742988146edc42f3","tid":2236352,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3caa073e1375bf00e4bdad7f733a3cac8707f4b3","tid":2236352,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:05:36.000Z","msg":"唔駛等2025<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}